{"tid":1918921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本政府確認3月15日起禁止高價轉售口罩","createTime":"2020-03-10T12:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T02:24:44.000Z","uid":192307,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ab0530da8dac181bef70f628f2f50835b1cd69","tid":1918921,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"根據日本經濟新聞3月10日11:50的報導，為打擊囤貨及高價轉賣口罩圖利等行為，日本政府確認修改《國民生活穩定緊急措施法》政令，禁止囤貨及高價轉賣口罩圖利。由3月15日起如違反相關法律，可能會被監禁1年及罰款100萬日圓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://r.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO56598980Q0A310C2EE8000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.nikkei.com%2Farticle%2FDGXMZO56598980Q0A310C2EE8000&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=926aceed\" target=\"_blank\">https://r.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO56598980Q0A310C2EE8000</a>"},{"pid":"67e5b5e72ced44c2f361a23e40a9b608d4ece671","tid":1918921,"uid":192307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"從一般消費者能夠拜訪的店舖或網路商店等購買口罩進行轉賣的人將會成為該禁令的懲處對象。"},{"pid":"d4e1709a70211e5774d23f4259e64b5e35503412","tid":1918921,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:03:19.000Z","msg":"禁止以比取得價格還要高的價格出售的原因，是為了防治以利益為目的的轉賣行為。商品本身價格設定的很便宜，但包含運費、手續費之後的整體價格卻十分昂貴的話則該業者將會成為懲處的對象。此外，在網拍用很便宜的價格起標，最後交易成立時的價格超過去得價格的話也算在違法的範圍內。"},{"pid":"c74b24e7865ddaff64b09c0a4f8c088668096312","tid":1918921,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n嘩零售商自己起價囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed76d0420c501e0e7db05bc01fb58849dff66d22","tid":1918921,"uid":23085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"果班讀過中六商業嘅人呢？"},{"pid":"c164f153f3e5c59de80510a8943620a84bc76125","tid":1918921,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c74b24e7865ddaff64b09c0a4f8c088668096312","tid":1918921,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":